btrplace.solver.choco

Class DefaultChocoReconfigurationAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • btrplace.solver.choco.DefaultChocoReconfigurationAlgorithm
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChocoReconfigurationAlgorithm, ChocoReconfigurationAlgorithmParams, ReconfigurationAlgorithm

    public class DefaultChocoReconfigurationAlgorithm
extends Object
implements ChocoReconfigurationAlgorithm
    Default implementation of ChocoReconfigurationAlgorithm. A same instance cannot be used to solve multiple problems simultaneously.

    By default, the algorithm relies on a SingleRunner solver.

    Author:
    Fabien Hermenier
